Query
inputs.value:
union pageViews,customEvents
| where timestamp between((now()-24h)..now())
| summarize Users=dcount(user_Id) by client_City, client_CountryOrRegion, bin(timestamp, 1h)
| order by timestamp asc
| render barchart

content.Query:
